  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A prototype colonoscope with an extra passively bending distal section has been developed by
      Olympus Japan (ref. publications). The present study (2006-2007) is testing refinements of
      this function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Results from the first prototype evaluation has been published.Modifications are presently
      evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
